  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add garlic and ginger, sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add onion, sauté until softened, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add Asian-chive-buchu, wilt into the onion mixture.",
    "Add spinach, cook until wilted.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Warm the corn husk wraps by wrapping them in a damp paper towel and microwaving for 20-30 seconds.",
    "Assemble the wraps by spooning the herbal mixture into the center of each wrap.",
    "Serve warm and enjoy."
